                                                                                                                               components are identified.
                                                                                                            3.11.7e[b]         Organizational systems and system components to include in a supply
                                                                                                                               chain risk management plan are identified.
                                                                                                            3.11.7e[c]         A plan for managing supply chain risks associated with organizational
